  "text": "The goitre incidence, calculated on the basis of the reference values proposed by Szybiński et al. [CITATION_1] , was also the highest in 1994 and was 66.6% (in girls and boys 75% and 59% respectively); in 1999, 9.7% (8.5% and 10.8%); in 2010, 4.4% (6.3% and 2%); and in 2016, 2.5% (0 and 5.7%). The values of goitre incidence are presented in Table I .",
